  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2022-04-11",
    "date": "2022-05-06T18:01:08Z",
    "text": "Protecting Gun Owners in Bankruptcy Act of 2022\n\nThis bill modifies federal bankruptcy law to allow an individual debtor to exempt from their bankruptcy estate one or more firearms up to a total maximum value of $3,000. The bill also specifies that such firearms are household goods that are not subject to liens in bankruptcy."
